{"tid":1063694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園酒店 25歲仔猝死房內","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T13:06:46.000Z","uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44e58f09d55033ba32f95e84157abeaa63766998","tid":1063694,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】海洋公園酒店一名25歲男住客，凌晨被發現在房間內猝死。<br />\n<br />\n現場為香港仔黃竹坑道180號海洋公園萬豪酒店。警方凌晨1時49分接獲職員報案，指懷疑事主在房內暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主當場被證實死亡。警方經初調查，相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/海洋公園酒店-25歲仔猝死房內-002600524.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-25%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E6%88%BF%E5%85%A7-002600524.html&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=b03ae096\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/海洋公園酒店-25歲仔猝死房內-002600524.html</a>"},{"pid":"7d786ceb80d28dcd2a417c3758879b18ae811749","tid":1063694,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"王百萬案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b8e8bcf21144967ca6dc50a560dbe06dc88bbc","tid":1063694,"uid":52490,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"開咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁快有命案 <br />\nBtw rip"},{"pid":"3e1cbdaaad2445f76a86bfe9c4bc6fe5782f6785","tid":1063694,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"打飛機猝死"},{"pid":"8b6e4aedeb955b7469895964af70f1d535b3f2ad","tid":1063694,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1cbdaaad2445f76a86bfe9c4bc6fe5782f6785","tid":1063694,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"打飛機猝死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"